            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">insert(Tree1 :: <a href="#t:tree/2">tree</a>(Key, Value))<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">Tree2</span></h1>




          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/gb_trees.erl#L320" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Tree1 = Tree2 = <a href="#t:tree/2">tree</a>(Key, Value)</pre>

        </div>


<p>Inserts <code class="inline">Key</code> with value <code class="inline">Value</code> into <code class="inline">Tree1</code>, returning the new
tree; raises an exception if <code class="inline">Key</code> is already present.</p><h2 id="insert/3-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#insert/3-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">Tree1</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">gb_trees</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_orddict</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-2">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-3">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-3">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-4">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-4">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="n">Tree2</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">gb_trees</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">insert</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-5">(</span><span class="ss">c</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Tree1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-5">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">gb_trees</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">to_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-6">(</span><span class="n">Tree2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-6">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-7">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-8">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-8">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-9">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-9">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-10">{</span><span class="ss">c</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-10">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2291050871-7">]</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
